&lt;h2 id="before-you-begin">Before you begin&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>To start fullstack development on your PC, you have two options&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>Install &lt;a href="https://ubuntu.com/download">Ubuntu&lt;/a>/&lt;a href="https://kubuntu.org/getkubuntu/">Kubuntu&lt;/a> (if you prefer KDE) - recomended way&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://chocolatey.org/install">Install chocolatley package manager&lt;/a> in Windows OS, or download and install all required packages manully&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h2 id="install-nodejs">Install NodeJS&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="tabs-0" role="tablist">&lt;li class="nav-item">
&lt;a class="nav-link active tab-Ubuntu"
id="tabs-0-0-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-0-0" role="tab" onclick="handleClick(&amp;#34;Ubuntu&amp;#34;);"
aria-controls="tabs-0-0" aria-selected="true">
Ubuntu
&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>&lt;li class="nav-item">
&lt;a class="nav-link tab-Windows"
id="tabs-0-1-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-0-1" role="tab" onclick="handleClick(&amp;#34;Windows&amp;#34;);"
aria-controls="tabs-0-1" aria-selected="false">
Windows
&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="tab-content" id="tabs-0-content">&lt;div class="tab-pane fade show active"
id="tabs-0-0" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-0-0-tab">&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code class="language-en" data-lang="en">curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_16.x | sudo -E bash -
sudo apt-get install -y nodejs
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="tab-pane fade"
id="tabs-0-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-0-1-tab">&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code class="language-en" data-lang="en"> choco install nodejs
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;h2 id="install-vscode">Install VSCode&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Build and debug modern web and cloud applications. Code is free and available on your favorite platform - Linux, Mac OSX, and Windows.&lt;/p>
&lt;ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="tabs-1" role="tablist">&lt;li class="nav-item">
&lt;a class="nav-link active tab-Ubuntu"
id="tabs-1-0-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-1-0" role="tab" onclick="handleClick(&amp;#34;Ubuntu&amp;#34;);"
aria-controls="tabs-1-0" aria-selected="true">
Ubuntu
&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>&lt;li class="nav-item">
&lt;a class="nav-link tab-Windows"
id="tabs-1-1-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-1-1" role="tab" onclick="handleClick(&amp;#34;Windows&amp;#34;);"
aria-controls="tabs-1-1" aria-selected="false">
Windows
&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="tab-content" id="tabs-1-content">&lt;div class="tab-pane fade show active"
id="tabs-1-0" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-1-0-tab">&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code class="language-en" data-lang="en">cd /tmp
wget -O vscode.deb &amp;#39;https://code.visualstudio.com/sha/download?build=stable&amp;amp;os=linux-deb-x64&amp;#39;
sudo apt install ./vscode.deb
rm -f vscode.deb
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="tab-pane fade"
id="tabs-1-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-1-1-tab">&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code class="language-en" data-lang="en"> choco install vscode
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;h2 id="install-postgresql">Install PostgreSQL&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>PostgreSQL is an object-relational database management system.&lt;/p>
&lt;ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="tabs-2" role="tablist">&lt;li class="nav-item">
&lt;a class="nav-link active tab-Ubuntu"
id="tabs-2-0-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-2-0" role="tab" onclick="handleClick(&amp;#34;Ubuntu&amp;#34;);"
aria-controls="tabs-2-0" aria-selected="true">
Ubuntu
&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>&lt;li class="nav-item">
&lt;a class="nav-link tab-Windows"
id="tabs-2-1-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-2-1" role="tab" onclick="handleClick(&amp;#34;Windows&amp;#34;);"
aria-controls="tabs-2-1" aria-selected="false">
Windows
&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="tab-content" id="tabs-2-content">&lt;div class="tab-pane fade show active"
id="tabs-2-0" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-2-0-tab">&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code class="language-en" data-lang="en"> sudo apt-get install -y postgresql postgresql-client
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="tab-pane fade"
id="tabs-2-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-2-1-tab">&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code class="language-en" data-lang="en"> choco install postgresql -y --params &amp;#39;/Password:test&amp;#39;
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;h2 id="install-dbeaver">Install DBeaver&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>DBeaver is free and open source universal database tool for developers and database administrators.&lt;/p>
&lt;ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="tabs-3" role="tablist">&lt;li class="nav-item">
&lt;a class="nav-link active tab-Ubuntu"
id="tabs-3-0-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-3-0" role="tab" onclick="handleClick(&amp;#34;Ubuntu&amp;#34;);"
aria-controls="tabs-3-0" aria-selected="true">
Ubuntu
&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>&lt;li class="nav-item">
&lt;a class="nav-link tab-Windows"
id="tabs-3-1-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-3-1" role="tab" onclick="handleClick(&amp;#34;Windows&amp;#34;);"
aria-controls="tabs-3-1" aria-selected="false">
Windows
&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="tab-content" id="tabs-3-content">&lt;div class="tab-pane fade show active"
id="tabs-3-0" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-3-0-tab">&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code class="language-en" data-lang="en">sudo add-apt-repository ppa:serge-rider/dbeaver-ce -y
sudo apt-get install dbeaver-ce -y
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="tab-pane fade"
id="tabs-3-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-3-1-tab">&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code class="language-en" data-lang="en"> choco install dbeaver -y
